The course acquaints students with basic Norwegian vocabulary, grammar and rules of spelling and pronunciation, as well as the basic facts about Norwegian culture, society and history.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The purpose of the course is to provide students with knowledge of practical Norwegian on the beginners' level.
The level of language competence is A1-A2, see: http://www.coe.int/t/dg4/linguistic/Manuel1_EN.asp#ManualLearning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After the completion of the course students:
 will be able to lead simple conversations in Norwegian;
read and understand simple Norwegian texts and speech;
have basic knowledge about Norwegian grammar;
have basic knowledge about Norwegian culture and society.
